{"tid":479268,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"死喇我中咗酒癮，救下我","createTime":"2017-11-25T02:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T02:49:30.000Z","uid":79502,"like":1,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f428807bf6f6e2b2652c0cdc7c24a943a96ecde7","tid":479268,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:34:54.000Z","msg":"幾個月前嘅我仲屌緊啤酒好苦好難飲，<br />\n近排生日後決定一試赤柱bar<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>，叫左杯Blanc，點知一試就上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11月5，D酒名全部唔識讀，好尷尬咁This this this，第一次醉，ringring地，好爽呀 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/101024_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F101024_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d07e586e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/101048_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F101048_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9bcd9c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/102511_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F102511_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e8bb6e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11月11，決定搵靚景再享受<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/102737_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F102737_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e27ce524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/102839_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F102839_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=89e06b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11月18，又係赤柱，其他啤酒名唔識讀就試咗呢杯叫Hoegaarden同Sea Breeze ，<br />\n正撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/102858_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F102858_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1180edd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98e26bde519cf473875a3e1f56af087cbb820c5a","tid":479268,"uid":103325,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"如果你有一日發現，你每晚都要飲醉至訓到，同埋一無酒飲就好唔舒服，咁就真係酒癮啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：真係有酒癮，而家戒緊"},{"pid":"8719905c128a3a2e163f6bcd8bf1b89f79472fef","tid":479268,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你有一日發現，你每晚都要飲醉至訓到，同埋一無酒飲就好唔舒服，咁就真係酒癮啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：真係有酒癮，而家戒緊</blockquote><br />\n點戒"},{"pid":"3cdd115ce9625c138f1022fcda7790ebbfb0d996","tid":479268,"uid":122331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你有一日發現，你每晚都要飲醉至訓到，同埋一無酒飲就好唔舒服，咁就真係酒癮啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：真係有酒癮，而家戒緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者突然斷酒嗰幾日會頭暈 痛 個人會燥啲<br />\n或者飲得越嚟越多<br />\n咁就真係酒癮"},{"pid":"015f3c79ac260285b4fc8c89fa700148f021b80c","tid":479268,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你有一日發現，你每晚都要飲醉至訓到，同埋一無酒飲就好唔舒服，咁就真係酒癮啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：真係有酒癮，而家戒緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者突然斷酒嗰幾日會頭暈 痛 個人會燥啲<br />\n或者飲得越嚟越多<br />\n咁就真係酒癮</blockquote><br />\n我而家起咗個頭"},{"pid":"e68195698b43c4172880e6972e4d704ae55e4c63","tid":479268,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"酒癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續飲"},{"pid":"f3769cb87f3c13dde825213b9d87e8f1eebf3a28","tid":479268,"uid":122331,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你有一日發現，你每晚都要飲醉至訓到，同埋一無酒飲就好唔舒服，咁就真係酒癮啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：真係有酒癮，而家戒緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者突然斷酒嗰幾日會頭暈 痛 個人會燥啲<br />\n或者飲得越嚟越多<br />\n咁就真係酒癮</blockquote><br />\n我而家起咗個頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好玩啦 咁都叫起咗個頭<br />\n得一兩杯啤酒 同班friend吹都唔止啦<br />\n<br />\n我係你就有得個post沉算"},{"pid":"db405617b280d832afdc37ef13f3e7bea64e420e","tid":479268,"uid":29080,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:45:43.000Z","msg":"原來只係曬命<br />\n快啲飲撚死佢啦"},{"pid":"4e782caa0009c2bed3e3df61201b244519d7e211","tid":479268,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:07:02.000Z","msg":"收錢打手收皮la"},{"pid":"8d505d8555c0996438e5bdede2b13878a8ea0abe","tid":479268,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來只係曬命<br />\n快啲飲撚死佢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁都叫曬命...?<br />\n<br />\n你究竟廢到咩地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1553e39a0974f76ede04edc9facdf753330aad1c","tid":479268,"uid":45431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你有一日發現，你每晚都要飲醉至訓到，同埋一無酒飲就好唔舒服，咁就真係酒癮啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：真係有酒癮，而家戒緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者突然斷酒嗰幾日會頭暈 痛 個人會燥啲<br />\n或者飲得越嚟越多<br />\n咁就真係酒癮</blockquote><br />\n我而家起咗個頭</blockquote><br />\n有節制好難有癮<br />\n對自己好啲，盡量飲啲好既酒，一杯cocktail兩三舊水，1shot 威士忌三四百蚊，你見到張單都好難有癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41e975e4bb600f64ca62a43c2ce07e459c5596b","tid":479268,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"你個幾杯算酒癮&hellip;我平時響屋企自對都唔止呢幾杯咁少"},{"pid":"e55e602030c2b02c5a03d09da44835fa6e635cbf","tid":479268,"uid":54994,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"19歲飲左8年幾到，無論晴天落雨，肚痛感冒，食藥都搵啤酒送，試過飲到急性酒精中毒失禁，最癲果時已經飲到無晒感覺，醉又醉唔晒，但愈黎愈難搵番酒醉咩都唔諗既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n好似係8月開始戒，依家可以飲可以唔飲，唔係朋友生日又或者出街食飯基本上都可以完全唔飲，最多知第日放假咪飲兩罐啤酒賀賀佢。<br />\n<br />\n至於方法&hellip;其實係我7月決定減肥之後開始有跳舞，跳完舞開頭都有飲，不過隨住個人開始慢慢瘦番d運動量又大左，好多時飲水都已經飽晒，仲邊有胃口飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自制力固然重要喇，但我戒果時又真係無咩癮，最多成日就訓果時都想飲番罐等自己好訓d(其實飲左你既睡眠質素先差)，大概半個月度已經無話想特別飲&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我試過飲番幾日，不過發現自己一飲就係咁追酒飲，所以之後都盡量唔飲酒。<br />\n<br />\n同埋有時諗番因為飲酒失去左既野(我因為飲醉同個朋友嘈完打交結果破左相)，就會發現其實飲黎好無謂，一大班朋友開心飲係ok既，但平時係唔係都係咁飲就真係好大問題"},{"pid":"9e60456087ae0b0e2d52f32cca2f66474054d2b0","tid":479268,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"洗咩戒<br />\n呢啲先係人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653f7a4dd1d121201e2c582c6f44a79b4076a866","tid":479268,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"無病呻吟"},{"pid":"356b511700aab80a83fb7c09aba7c96b694b3b5c","tid":479268,"uid":57962,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68a3d357f7937ce372abf89cc0c74f03501e46b2","tid":479268,"uid":10214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"傻鳩先戒酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2dfb20125fef80a2f26e732e6da833202cf315","tid":479268,"uid":148599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"唔好飲啤酒啦，飲wiskey，做完野夜晚飲返杯真係鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b636533064e2ca1fedc8d7c593809b689a0de3d","tid":479268,"uid":82717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻鳩先戒酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔係咁講，好多人飲到痛風或有病先被迫要戒酒。<br />\n我唔會儲酒，但會每樣有些少，好似紅酒白酒汽泡酒啤酒whisky，希望健健康康keep住有酒飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b02601fb38b9d52dee91823eba436864d38956","tid":479268,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好飲啤酒啦，飲wiskey，做完野夜晚飲返杯真係鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平價wiskey點入手"},{"pid":"7261d53ed1dc05f24e34de975b135a2b2a7d9a9b","tid":479268,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好飲啤酒啦，飲wiskey，做完野夜晚飲返杯真係鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平價wiskey點入手</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecd48025664a56aaaacd61999da7b82390fe921","tid":479268,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好飲啤酒啦，飲wiskey，做完野夜晚飲返杯真係鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平價wiskey點入手</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/476765/3?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/476765/3?ref=android</a><br />\n歡迎入坑"},{"pid":"564387b3c268f0cace5235dff48b981ed11af28d","tid":479268,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a68d770b14961b6924b327f8d81613b7c01574","tid":479268,"uid":17705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好飲啤酒啦，飲wiskey，做完野夜晚飲返杯真係鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平價wiskey點入手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本買蘇威平， duty free, 香港就深水埗世光"},{"pid":"ccbd54f62e1f58fae151bd3c9d1c6deccc15